premise_source_doc_sentence: Henry John Deutschendorf Jr.  (  December 31 , 1943 -- October 12 , 1997  )  , known professionally as John Denver , an American musician , singer-songwriter , record producer , activist , actor , and humanitarian , whose greatest commercial success was as a solo singer .

`` Take Me Home , Country Roads '' is a song written by Bill Danoff , Taffy Nivert and John Denver that was derived from a poem written in a letter to them by their friend , John Albert Fitzgerald who was residing in West Virginia at the time .
